commands.name: local:restart
commands.script: npm run local:stop && npm run local:start

commands.name: local:reset
commands.script: npm run local:clean && npm run local:start

commands.name: test:unit
commands.script: npm run test --workspace=frontend && npm run test --workspace=backend && npm run test --workspace=scripts

commands.name: test:unit:coverage
commands.script: npm run test:coverage --workspace=frontend && npm run test:coverage --workspace=backend && npm run test:coverage --workspace=scripts

commands.name: test:e2e:debug
commands.script: cd tests/e2e && DEBUG=true HEADLESS=false npm test

commands.name: studio:dev-setup
commands.script: npm run reset-data --workspace=scripts-data --workspace=scripts-studios && npm run seed --workspace=scripts --workspace=scripts-studios --scenario studio-diverse && npm run validate --workspace=scripts/documentation-analysis --workspace=scripts/documentation-analysis-studios

commands.name: studio:quick-test
commands.script: npm run seed --workspace=scripts --workspace=scripts-studios --scenario minimal && npm run test:studio:unit

commands.name: studio:full-test
commands.script: npm run studio:dev-setup && npm run test:studio && npm run studio-health

commands.name: test:all
commands.script: npm run test:unit && npm run test:integration && npm run test:e2e

commands.name: validate:all
commands.script: npm run test:final-integration && npm run validate --workspace=scripts/documentation-analysis --workspace=scripts/documentation-analysis:cross-platform && npm run validate --workspace=scripts/documentation-analysis --workspace=scripts/documentation-analysis:parity

commands.name: local:start:secure
commands.script: npm run security:validate && npm run local:start

commands.name: local:emergency-stop
commands.script: docker-compose -f devtools/docker/docker-compose.local.yml down --remove-orphans && docker network prune -f

commands.name: build:analyze
commands.script: npm run build && npm run validate --workspace=scripts/documentation-analysis --workspace=scripts/documentation-analysis:build

commands.name: lint
commands.description: Lints code for style and errors
